# /gstack-upgrade

`/gstack-upgrade` is now a compatibility alias.

Use `/nexus-upgrade` as the canonical command.

Compatibility rules:
- do not define an independent upgrade contract here
- do not diverge from the Nexus upgrade workflow
- route users to `/nexus-upgrade` for the real install detection, upgrade, and changelog flow

If an older workflow invokes `/gstack-upgrade`, tell the user:

> `/gstack-upgrade` is a compatibility alias. Running the canonical `/nexus-upgrade` flow instead.

Then follow the exact workflow defined in `nexus-upgrade/SKILL.md`.
